{"tid":2222560,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"亞美尼亞阿塞拜疆兩國持續交戰 聯合國安理會將開緊急會議","createTime":"2020-09-29T07:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T17:48:53.000Z","uid":60545,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9f763ecf019ee1f1d1de35918bed0e28a892ef13","tid":2222560,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:31:19.000Z","msg":"亞塞拜然境內亞美尼亞族分離主義分子掌控的納哥諾卡拉巴克地區（Nagorny Karabakh）週末爆發激烈戰鬥，外交官員今天說，聯合國安全理事會明天將舉行閉門緊急會議。<br />\n<br />\n法新社報導，外交官員說，會議將在格林威治時間21時（台北時間30日凌晨5時）舉行。法國與德國敦促將緊急會議列入議程後，比利時正式提出要求。<br />\n<br />\n非常任理事國愛沙尼亞早在27日強調，必須對納哥諾卡拉巴克地區爆發致命衝突召開緊急會議。<br />\n<br />\n外交官員說，英國也加入歐洲國家行列推動舉行會談；這些官員又說，會議結束後，安理會將發表聯合聲明，如果沒有達成全體共識，將由歐洲會員國發表。<br />\n<br />\n這場衝突是在年度聯合國大會期間爆發，外界擔憂高加索地區的亞塞拜然與亞美尼亞將發生戰爭；這兩個國家都曾是前蘇聯的加盟共和國。<br />\n<br />\n納哥諾卡拉巴克地區在亞塞拜然境內，但由亞美尼亞族分離主義勢力掌控，亞美尼亞與亞塞拜然陷入領土爭議衝突數十年，今年稍早與2016年曾爆發致命戰鬥。<br />\n<br />\n亞塞拜然與亞美尼亞部隊今天持續交戰、造成更多人喪亡，在國際呼籲這兩個宿敵停火時，但土耳其仍發表好戰言論。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯與亞美尼亞有軍事結盟，土耳其則支持亞塞拜然。<br />\n<br />\n根據可取得的最新數據，最近的戰鬥造成至少95人死亡，包括11名平民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4896406?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F4896406%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catebreaknews_ch2&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXC8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=d720eb42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/4896406?from=udn-catebreaknews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"546fc0ed3874689db51a085f0ae67c1dc0f9f177","tid":2222560,"uid":144626,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"垃圾聯合國"},{"pid":"5f8d7703dab09db38e5e2362d34df4c6a8c1f2e6","tid":2222560,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:37:46.000Z","msg":"土俄之戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97cc33787c5309a48e000cd6fbcfc1c3a86819d","tid":2222560,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T07:44:18.000Z","msg":"國際聯盟出手啦，世界和平啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9009906bfe6642ca7fbdabac32ecca5e11ef40","tid":2222560,"uid":197125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:07:30.000Z","msg":"其實上幾次都係打4日，今次會唔會係1號自動停火？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c476df7842ea05f4e3469a02adef73e2ed77272a","tid":2222560,"uid":38405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:09:17.000Z","msg":"un eat shit la"},{"pid":"ae7138f9d86dd0bc3f7b73bc16f9459c3e6f2e5f","tid":2222560,"uid":265881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:10:17.000Z","msg":"聯合國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"778d8435eef480ec96d55aae522e4155b06ae5f6","tid":2222560,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:11:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d3fa4236c957b371e97c727f0596745b50585a0","tid":2222560,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"土耳其其實想點<br />\n又同俄國買s400又撩俄國盟友打"},{"pid":"cc9ef23dac096a5435ceb5e94f5ac2081a66759a","tid":2222560,"uid":266342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:25:48.000Z","msg":"中共侵略香港<br />\n又唔見你個仆街開緊急會議<br />\n<br />\n垃圾組織"},{"pid":"f0b66fdd1a6d46f1ceb829e33873cfdf91fdbc27","tid":2222560,"uid":284794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T16:28:23.000Z","msg":"宗教戰爭"},{"pid":"be4fb67e90e44102091d52e843602ea1e4614fc1","tid":2222560,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f8d7703dab09db38e5e2362d34df4c6a8c1f2e6","tid":2222560,"uid":71508,"like":0,"disl